OL,3,CMan fined #4,000 for 'river rage'
OL,4,Cafter steering boat through regatta on
OL,5,CThames
OL,7,FA man who shouted abuse and nearly
OL,8,Fcrashed into rowers during a regatta
OL,9,Fon the River Thames has had to pay
OL,10,Fmore than #4,000 for his "river rage",
OL,11,Fthe Environment Agency said.
OL,13,FScott Keen steered his unregistered
OL,14,Fboat into the Kingston Amateur Regatta
OL,15,Fin July 2024, with video footage
OL,16,Fcapturing his "dangerous" behaviour.
OL,18,FKeen ignored umpire instructions and
OL,19,Fcut across the racing line, where he
OL,20,Fnearly collided with rowers, the
OL,21,FEnvironment Agency said.
