OL,7,FHe proceeded to steer his boat through
OL,8,Fthe regatta, before getting caught in
OL,9,Fthe anchor rope of a race boat,
OL,10,Fprompting him to start shouting and
OL,11,Fswearing at the competitors that they
OL,12,F"did not own the ... water", the
OL,13,Fagency added.
