OL,3,CMan fined #4,000 for 'river rage'
OL,4,Cafter steering boat through regatta on
OL,5,CThames
OL,7,FKeen, of Morden, Surrey, was found
OL,8,Fguilty at Staines Magistrates' Court
OL,9,Ffor obstructing a boat race,
OL,10,Finterfering with the safety of others,
OL,11,Fusing abusive language towards
OL,12,Fofficials and volunteers, failing to
OL,13,Fcomply with a harbour master's notice
OL,14,Fand failing to register his boat.
