OL,3,CMan fined #4,000 for 'river rage'
OL,4,Cafter steering boat through regatta on
OL,5,CThames
OL,7,F"An appalling incident of river rage
OL,8,Fon the River Thames at Kingston upon
OL,9,FThames in July 2024 has ended with
OL,10,F#4,334.54 in fines, compensation and
OL,11,Fcosts at Staines Magistrates' Court on
OL,12,FJanuary 28 2025," the Environment
OL,13,FAgency said.
OL,15,FMaria Herlihy, of the Environment
OL,16,FAgency added: "This incident was a
OL,17,Fdisgrace. Keen showed no regard for
OL,18,Fthe safety of other river users and
OL,19,Fcould easily have caused a tragedy.
