OL,3,CMan fined #4,000 for 'river rage'
OL,4,Cafter steering boat through regatta on
OL,5,CThames
OL,7,F"Quite frankly, it was no surprise to
OL,8,Fdiscover that his boat was
OL,9,Funregistered, and we are happy with
OL,10,Fthe court result.
OL,12,F"We hope that this serves as a clear
OL,13,Fwarning to all ` anti-social and
OL,14,Fdangerous behaviour on our rivers will
OL,15,Fnot be tolerated, and we will take
OL,16,Frobust action to deal with those who
OL,17,Fdisregard the rules and regulations
OL,18,Ffor boating on the River Thames."
